c5 c3\">Status Timeline</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c1\">IMPORTANT NOTE: The app does NOT need to be connected once the program is running. Once a program is running the app can be shut down, even the device can be shut down and it will not affect the program running on the controller. &nbsp;You can re-launch the app and reconnect at any time to check the status, pause or stop a program</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c1\">The status timeline shows the entire program from left to right with a vertical bar showing where the program currently is in time.</span></p><p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\"></span></p><p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c1 c4\">Share your behind the scenes:</span><span class=\"c1\">&nbsp;launches the camera so you can take a shot of your awesome location and set up and post to social media (Thank you! We love seeing the systems in action)</span></p></body></html>";

